The Incheon District Prosecutors ' Office sent a team of some 40 investigators to Geumsuwon in Gyeonggi Province , the location of the headquarters of a religious sect allegedly led by Yoo 's family .
Prosecutors believe Yoo is hiding out at the headquarters and have stepped up monitoring and patrol efforts with the police .
